name: Fake Profile
overview: Camila meets her Prince Charming through a dating app. After an idyllic romance, she plans to surprise him — only to end up trapped in a false paradise.

episodes.name: Flesh and Bone
episodes.overview: Camila is swept off her feet by handsome Fernando. After a dreamy night out, they end up at his hotel suite… unaware they’re being watched.

episodes.name: Panic in Paradise
episodes.overview: A misunderstanding allows for Camila and David to move into Riviera Esmeralda. Pedro tests Miguel. Camila is hell-bent on uncovering the truth.

episodes.name: Even If It Hurts
episodes.overview: Camila is furious after finding out what’s making the rounds online. David questions her desire to stay. A question from Lucas catches her off guard.

episodes.name: Breathless
episodes.overview: Ángela extracts a promise from Lucas, but what he asks in return startles her. Pedro tells Tina that Miguel has taken the bait. Camila acts dismissively.

episodes.name: Dangerous Images
episodes.overview: The incident at Camila’s home triggers vivid flashbacks for her. Lucas warns Ángela about what the police might find. Pedro calls a meeting.

episodes.name: Red Velvet's Secret
episodes.overview: Ángela makes a decision about her marriage. Visions of Inti haunt Adrián. One of Miguel’s past lovers shares intimate details of their relationship.

episodes.name: Inside the Wolf's Mouth
episodes.overview: Someone surprising comes to Camila’s defense. Inti’s seduction attempts persist. Camila leaves a party alone — and puts herself in imminent danger.

episodes.name: Temptation in the Dark
episodes.overview: Ángela becomes increasingly cynical. Camila receives a word of caution from an unlikely character. Cris spices things up with Adrián.

episodes.name: Night of the Executioners
episodes.overview: Camila refuses to assist with an event, and is promptly reminded of what’s at stake if she doesn’t. What Pedro discovers provokes a hellish response.
